    },
    {
        "content": "<p>alexcrichton created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12712#discussion_r2880913282\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>This feels a bit too strong even for debug assertions since this is basically quadratic behavior. I think it's probably fine to defer this to tests detecting situations like this.</p>\n<p>Basically I think it's fine for debug mode to have extra checks, but changing big-O I think should still be avoided.</p>\n</blockquote>",
