    {
        "content": "<p>fitzgen created <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/12712#discussion_r2881599913\">PR review comment</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>That method does exist, but it goes through and deallocates each node in the map within the context of the forest. But since the forest isn't shared across multiple maps in this case, that is wasted work, and simply clearing the whole forest and replacing our map with the new/empty/default map is faster and simpler.</p>\n</blockquote>",
        "id": 577124061,
        "sender_full_name": "Wasmtime GitHub notifications bot",
        "timestamp": 1772594999
    },
